    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Iunoni <expan><abbr>Reg</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Petronius <lb n="4"/>Tertius |(centurio) <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>I <expan><abbr>Ger</abbr><ex>manorum</ex></expan> ex voto <lb n="6"/>suscepto pro <lb n="7"/>se et suis pos<lb break="no" n="8"/>uit <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Vermutlich verschleppt aus Jagsthausen. Der Stein war lange Zeit n der Kirche von Olnhausen als Kämpfer im nördlichen Chorbogen vermauert. Autopsie R. Wiegels. Hauptbearbeiterin B. Esch.</p>
            </div>
